				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">You write the high, then low byte of the address of the attribute byte you want to update to $2006, then you write the byte you want written to that attribute byte to $2007. This must be done during vblank or while rendering is disabled. 
<br />
<br />
<br />See this for the addresses: <!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://wiki.nesdev.com/w/index.php/PPU_attribute_tables">http://wiki.nesdev.com/w/index.php/PPU_attribute_tables</a><!-- m --></div>

